{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>ViuTV劇集《IT狗2.0》今晚（1日）播出第五集，影帝古天樂驚喜客串，他在劇中飾演「綿登主腦」綿住尼，與凌文龍飾演的葉念信上演一場關乎全港網絡生死存亡的終極談判，劇情更融入古天樂分別在《尋秦記》中飾演的項少龍及在《九龍城寨》中飾演的龍捲風兩大經典角色，火速掀起網民熱議！</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127027262382673920237481.jpeg/zr6Edtis2N5dpHWG_RLCBpinWyP1s9hcOaP9Gzmj_Rs\" alt=\"影帝古天樂驚喜客串《IT狗2.0》！（IG@viutv）\"><figcaption>影帝古天樂驚喜客串《IT狗2.0》！（IG@viutv）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028118956281856932856.jpeg/0iqPE_y-wcDTD-ez2raoc0rR4-ZghWmMmHNeu5hzXrs\" alt=\"霸氣登場！（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>霸氣登場！（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028116611534848420159.jpeg/jpbiKjzG8UlhRlCuSf2w0Rs1LJPF014GSgGgp0oBoKc\" alt=\"霸氣登場！（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>霸氣登場！（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028114111598592890457.jpeg/0zYVze6S31D-CdgmQ2Y2bcMTAFfDBbmi0w7GStMOxko\" alt=\"飾演「綿登主腦」綿住尼。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>飾演「綿登主腦」綿住尼。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028249093214208048639.jpeg/b8mkGy0TqaYXiwJgNENJ_9vN2yPq5wXcV18AO1dfADs\" alt=\"談判。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>談判。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028246572306432208915.jpeg/MJddsVKPMFbtSa1PFnmRO4VLzv4rmf2Gg_qSfoP6kn4\" alt=\"談判。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>談判。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028244382748672837640.jpeg/i2lXdBJglsizPo8GdOF4WfFdIpmghLdVbO8hP2zvIT8\" alt=\"談判。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>談判。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028242155442176372965.jpeg/M0u-ga16WPRslOs2Pkr_VRBFHOdUgf34jTbyQY028kE\" alt=\"重現經典金句。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>重現經典金句。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127028239554842624698741.jpeg/gBtph6n8s-UcmQGPbxDvy4BOrelTV9qIb7UWvG-1Frw\" alt=\"重現經典金句。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>重現經典金句。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><p>劇情講到當阿信（凌文龍飾）見到綿住尼（古天樂飾）時，即被對方嚇親，口窒窒問道：「龍……項少龍？」兩人你一言我一語談判相當精彩，而彭秀慧飾演的Cathy Ho介入調停，坦言Louis雖然不相信Web3技術，但堅信AI與加密貨幣才是未來發展方向，綿住尼更抛出震撼金句：「AI係人類通往Web3嘅唯一一條鎖匙，但係AI亦都係人類最後一個發明。」網民紛紛留言激讚古天樂驚喜客串型到爆，更迅即在各大社交平台引發洗版式熱烈討論：「真係大癲」、「古生真係型爆」！</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127029144174071808807362.jpeg/jw9l05l0y7T5DqV5ALc3nuo76qilez1brjP09q4z9PY\" alt=\"嚇窒。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>嚇窒。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127029141804158976183065.jpeg/aqqIBQ609rDqiFc4cY4Bsz3MSZ_phqawrj8a4K4_GuA\" alt=\"綿住尼。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>綿住尼。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127029105029025792650843.jpeg/Lkv-720HzPb762y9PUWCbqZet-yNT50FsxABTrMQAU4\" alt=\"我係龍捲風！（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>我係龍捲風！（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127029102768164864825017.jpeg/mRZG66jwORUGtajqwykA_kmF2tVkJU5VDE-ooAxPqKA\" alt=\"驚喜！（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>驚喜！（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127029100461166592601347.jpeg/rsTfL1uac23BIqQZNBqSsxAVtAmzyQgGNlHv0jZR79I\" alt=\"彭秀慧調停。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>彭秀慧調停。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127029098133196800908145.jpeg/PDO1DzYrQ_nhEbiS6aS9B3ZNVOp8Osjgj-qhb4_qoW8\" alt=\"彭秀慧調停。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>彭秀慧調停。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127029095763283968892635.jpeg/wmvqagIZAJoI_meerDIY0kvToeyhYjtG99qw_vfasP4\" alt=\"彭秀慧調停。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>彭秀慧調停。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127030247209177088683907.jpeg/2XTb3FrkM1YDdu6hfAG2JVOu3CcSiGiJdk97lHZPe5Q\" alt=\"金句。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>金句。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127030244835069952013629.jpeg/tTjq67lipKrPfqt-4V2Psmx_4Xzcjk5u8FuFTfBbhU0\" alt=\"金句。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>金句。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127030242641317888274163.jpeg/EpHKpvK4l8-V-COQulyZ5Tf_11OX9i6vOD7mwzg-5sM\" alt=\"凌文龍飾演阿信。（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>凌文龍飾演阿信。（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127030240216879104376548.jpeg/eMcYZcljOUnmMKZdiHaM7fbi2Be2GKsg2axPF9msTxc\" alt=\"霸氣！（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>霸氣！（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T16:23:51.880435+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":620,"images":20,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}